Not less than five thousand kids (aged 9-15) turned up for this year mPulse Planet  which held on Friday August 23, 2019 at  Landmark Event Centre, VI, Lagos. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1247602" src="https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/MTN-Mpulse.jpg?resize=640%2C853&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="640" height="853" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/MTN-Mpulse.jpg?w=750&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/MTN-Mpulse.jpg?resize=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1 225w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/MTN-Mpulse.jpg?resize=44%2C58&amp;ssl=1 44w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/MTN-Mpulse.jpg?resize=146%2C194&amp;ssl=1 146w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/MTN-Mpulse.jpg?resize=98%2C130&amp;ssl=1 98w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/MTN-Mpulse.jpg?resize=560%2C747&amp;ssl=1 560w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> From 8:00 am when the doors opened till 6:30 pm when the last kid and parent stepped out, it was fun after fun and there was no dull moment, no ebbs and it was delightful thrill all the way. The first delight as you step into the venue was a step into  a time portal that projected you from 2019 to the year 2044. Some of the coolest  kids from around the country came around to join in on the fun at  the mPulse planet. With a ‘bajillion’ exciting games, kids were treated to the best of games. One of the things that  made the event really thrilling was that everywhere you turned to, there was an adorable kid laughing or having fun. Another  unforgettable thing, was that the kids were super-eager to try their hands at new things such as the ‘Who Can Be A Millionaire’ styled radio show that allowed them flex their knowledge skills. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1247604" src="https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=640%2C427&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=58%2C39&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=260%2C173&amp;ssl=1 260w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=195%2C130&amp;ssl=1 195w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=115%2C77&amp;ssl=1 115w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?resize=560%2C373&amp;ssl=1 560w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/unnamed18.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Some other attractions at the planet include the Tech Town,  the famous Mekamon and many more. Alongside excited faces and fun games, mPulse Planet proved that there’s a budding genius in every home. The sheer talent displayed by the youngsters as they learnt and played was remarkable. It was particularly exhilarating because mPulse is designed to support our young geniuses as they take off and discover new heights. Thousands of kids converged at the Landmark Event Centre, VI, Lagos, on Thursday, August 23, 2018, for the launch of MTN Nigeria’s newest proposition, mPulse, targeted at Nigerian tweens and teens ranging from age nine to sixteen. August 26, 2018 In "Showtime People" MTN mPulse, the latest innovation from the leading ICT company, MTN Nigeria, made its debut today, Thursday 23rd August at the Landmark Events Centre, Victoria Island, Lagos. The proposition designed for tweens and teens (ages 9-15) will enable them learn and gain useful skills while having fun. August 24, 2018 In "News" A lot of us dream of having artworks of ourselves, some even go to the extent of hiring artistes just to experience the wonder of somebody sketching up an image of them. That is the extent at which humans value well sculpted images of themselves. September 30, 2018 In "News"